snippet.title: Slay the Princess – Halloween '22 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A spooky season demands a spooky trailer.

Keep your eyes peeled for some quick teasers of what's to come in the full release, and check out the Slay the Princess trailer as part of Steam Next Fest from October 3rd to October 10th.

Art and Animation done by Abby Howard.

Trailer edited by Tony Howard-Arias.

Voice acting by Jonathan Sims and Nichole Goodnight.

Music by Brandon Boone.

Slay the Princess was created by Tony Howard-Arias and Abby Howard.

Get Slay the Princess on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1989270/Slay_the_Princess/
